        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Big Basin State Park</name>
        <description>Santa Cruz METRO runs seasonal service on Line 35B from Cavallaro Transit Center in Scotts Valley to Big Basin State Park. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; https://scmetro.org/routes/route-35/ &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;SEASONAL SERVICE - SUMMER ONLY</description>
